OL,3,C'We've escaped from hell': The town at
OL,4,Cthe centre of fighting in Ukraine
OL,6,FITV News Correspondent John Ray
OL,7,Freports from the Ukrainian town of
OL,8,FVovchansk, where desperate attempts
OL,9,Fhave been made to rescue civilians
OL,10,Ffrom the frontline
OL,12,FThe last few miles are taken at break-
OL,13,Fneck speed through lanes and fields.
OL,15,FAhead, smoke rises from Vovchansk, the
OL,16,Ftown at the centre of ten days of
OL,17,Ffighting.
OL,19,FIt's our destination. We've joined a
OL,20,Frescue mission with the local police,
OL,21,Fbut our convoy is a target too.
