OL,3,C'We've escaped from hell': The town at
OL,4,Cthe centre of fighting in Ukraine
OL,6,FA small group of civilians are waiting
OL,7,Ffor us, hiding under the trees by the
OL,8,Fside of the road to shield them from
OL,9,FRussian drones. We can hear one
OL,10,Fbuzzing overhead; it is just one of
OL,11,Fmany terrors they have faced.
OL,13,FQuickly, the evacuees are bundled into
OL,14,Fpolice vehicles.
OL,16,FRaisa Zemovska's face is cut. There's
OL,17,Fa wound on her hand. But it's not the
OL,18,Fworst she has suffered.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/6
