OL,3,C'We've escaped from hell': The town at
OL,4,Cthe centre of fighting in Ukraine
OL,6,FHer name was Victoria, and they were
OL,7,Fmarried for 40 years. I ask where she
OL,8,Fis now.
OL,10,F"I had to bury her in the vegetable
OL,11,Fgarden. I told the police, but they
OL,12,Fsaid they couldn't come," he says.
OL,13,F"They said, just bury her yourself."
OL,15,FUkraine claimed today it still
OL,16,Fcontrols 60% of Vovchansk. But their
OL,17,Frescue operations suggest that hold is
OL,18,Fat best tenuous.
OL,20,FFor Raisa, we arrange a phone call
OL,21,Fwith her son.
