OL,3,C'We've escaped from hell': The town at
OL,4,Cthe centre of fighting in Ukraine
OL,6,F"We are alive - and we're in one
OL,7,Fpiece," she tells him. "We've escaped
OL,8,Ffrom hell."
OL,10,FBut her husband lies among the many
OL,11,Fdead in the town they left behind.
